deck: A 17 year old gun trigger user from the Tachikawa Branch
description:
Abilities

Izumi is a shooter white trigger user, unlike most other shooters he does not use a gun. Instead of firing trion bullets via a gun. He instead directly forms his trion into a cube and shoots it.

Like other shooter types Izuma can use multiple modes that changes the uses and effects of his bullets.

  • Hound-Bullets that track down and follow the target.
  • Viper-Bullets that form lines and can course the course via sharp turns and angles.
  • Asteroid-Standard bullets.
  • Meteor- Bullets that cause an explosion effecting a large area.
name: Kohei Izumi

description:
Origin

In the year 1066, a local nun named Areala was chased by a group of Vikings. Before the Vikings could slay her, a valkyrie appeared and stopped the Vikings. Disgusted by the actions of the Vikings, the valkyrie renounced her devotion to Odin and instead chose to serve "the only true God". The valkyrie empowered Areala with her spirit, thus giving her the strength to fight against the Vikings.

deck: The original Diana Prince. She looks pretty much like Wonder woman.
description:
In the forties, when Wonder Woman came to the "mans world", she wanted to be near Steve Trevor. She met Diana Prince, a nurse at the hospital Trevor was in. Prince wanted to go to her fiancee who moved to South America, but couldn`t, because the couple didn`t have enough money for Prince's plane ticket.

Wonder Woman paid her in exchange for her identity. She went off to lead her life Wonder woman had a secret identity.

Later, the first Diana Prince returned to reclaim her previous identity. But, due to some troubles with Nazis, she decided to leave again. She got a new identity: Diana White.
